title: Verify that when a new file is upload to a GCS bucket, a notification is generate at the Pub/Sub channel.
custom_summary: Verify that when a new file is upload to a GCS bucket, a notification is generate at the Pub/Sub channel.
custom_steps:
- Upload a new UCI score file to the chosen GCS bucket.
- Check if Pub/Sub channel receive notification
custom_expected:
- UEBA exports a UCI file from Mongo and then uploads to the GCS. After the file is uploaded to the GCS, a corresponding notification is dispatched to pub/sub.
- A notification should be received on the Pub/Sub channel after the upload.
